# ─── Data / AI artifacts (never commit dumps, fixtures with real data, or eval outputs) ─
*.parquet
*.pkl
*.pickle
*.duckdb
*.sqlite
*.db
data/raw/
data/processed/
# NOTE: keep a small fixture CSV/JSON by force-adding: git add -f tests/fixtures/x.json

# ─── Claude Code tooling ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Personal dev tooling (agents/hooks/rules/skills) — kept out of the repo so the
# 13 source files stay the visual center of gravity. CLAUDE.md and settings.json
# are tracked (they document project conventions and are useful to a reviewer).
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/agents/
.claude/hooks/
.claude/rules/
.claude/skills/
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
